{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1677-06_035", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour Monsieur. Sonnet"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Nouveau Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", juin 1677 (tome IV), p. 35-37"}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/note[1]", "tag": "note", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/note[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il existe une autre édition parisienne, réalisée \"Suivant la Copie imprimée\" par Claude Barbin, dont la pagination diffère."}], "attributes": {"resp": "editor"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[2]", "text": "."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Monsieur le Comte de Bregy dont je vous ay parlé dans ma Lettre precedente a fait le Sonnet qui suit pour Son Altesse Royale. Je croy que vous n’aurez pas de peine à luy donner la mesme approbation qu’il a reçeuë icy de tout le monde."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "POUR MONSIEUR, "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[2]", "text": "SONNET"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Tu serviras d’exemple un jour à nos Neveux,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Digne Frere d’un Roy le plus grand Roy du monde ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "S’il passe les Cesars, ta Valeur le seconde,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Et soûtient ses Lauriers par des Exploits fameux."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "A tes traits delicats, à ton air gracieux,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Tu sembles estre né pour une paix profonde ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Et dans le Champ de Mars dés que le Canon gronde,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Ton cœur anime tout, ton bras frape en tous lieux."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "A present qu’apres-toy tu fais marcher la Gloire,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Que tu ne combats point sans avoir la Victoire,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Louis"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "n’est plus le seul qui triomphe de tous ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais luy seul toute-fois des Princes de la Terre,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "De ceux qui sont en paix, ou qui nous font la guerre,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Peut voir tes grands Exploits sans en estre jaloux."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}]}